One approach to one's
career could be, well, I

00:12:18.070 --> 00:12:21.700
want to become an insert title.

00:12:21.700 --> 00:12:22.750
I want to be a director.

00:12:22.750 --> 00:12:25.480
I want to be a VP, or
I want to be a manager.

00:12:25.480 --> 00:12:29.920
Well, that's all good and
all, but how do you get?

00:12:29.920 --> 00:12:32.590
How do you actually
achieve those goals?

00:12:32.590 --> 00:12:36.500
And the answer is you
need to have the skills.

00:12:36.500 --> 00:12:38.590
You need to have the
skills, and then you

00:12:38.590 --> 00:12:41.320
need to actually
accomplish the work

00:12:41.320 --> 00:12:45.380
to earn the title of
whatever it is that you want.

00:12:45.380 --> 00:12:51.730
So the skills piece
here is something

00:12:51.730 --> 00:12:57.640
that when I think about this
mental checklist concept--

