My father taught me
how to play golf.

00:13:03.850 --> 00:13:05.620
I'm also a musician.

00:13:05.620 --> 00:13:12.490
And so when I learned how
to play baseball and golf,

00:13:12.490 --> 00:13:14.530
it's all about a checklist.

