00:13:39.760 --> 00:13:45.130
And shooting, for me,
it's an easy way for me

00:13:45.130 --> 00:13:47.740
to overlay an
existing framework,

00:13:47.740 --> 00:13:49.180
this checklist framework.

00:13:49.180 --> 00:13:50.830
I overlay that
checklist framework

00:13:50.830 --> 00:13:52.013
when I'm shooting as well.

00:13:52.013 --> 00:13:53.680
AUSTIN WILKINS: I was
watching the show,

00:13:53.680 --> 00:13:55.780
