I noticed how it kind
of helped you overcome

00:13:58.240 --> 00:14:00.640
the ambiguity that you mentioned
earlier, because you had

00:14:00.640 --> 00:14:03.760
this checklist, especially with
the atlatl competition you did.

00:14:03.760 --> 00:14:04.510
CHRIS CHENG: Yeah.

00:14:04.510 --> 00:14:08.320
So for those of you who don't
know what Austin just said,

00:14:08.320 --> 00:14:10.080
the word was "atlatl."

00:14:10.080 --> 00:14:13.410
